网络安全:httponly

  PHP中的设置 
    session.cookie_httponly = True
     <?php ini_set("session.cookie_httponly", 1); 
	 // or session_set_cookie_params(0, NULL, NULL, NULL, TRUE); 
	 ?>  
  利用HTTP-only Cookie缓解XSS之痛 
    http://netsecurity.51cto.com/art/200902/111143.htm
